---
title: Speedy Plant-Based Ground Protein Chili with Ciabatta Croutons
description: This delicious plant-based ground protein chili comes together in no time! We've packed it with warming spices, hearty beans and plenty of fresh veggies to satisfy the whole family on a chilly night.
